<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Nujood changed her name to Nujoom which means &quot;the stars in the sky&quot;; her former name means &quot;hidden one&quot;; so this is empowering her.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Nujood changed her name to Nujoom which means "the stars in the sky"; her former name means "hidden one"; so this is empowering her.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
